---
// Neumi 樂享系統首頁
---
<html lang="zh-Hant">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Neumi 樂享系統 | 自動化健康與護膚事業</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-50 text-slate-900">

    <header class="bg-indigo-900 text-white py-20 px-6">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold mb-6 tracking-tight">Neumi 樂享系統</h1>
            <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-medium mb-8 text-indigo-200">30 秒的日常習慣，帶來全新改變</p>
            <div class="bg-indigo-800 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-indigo-700 mb-10 text-left">
                <p class="text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed text-indigo-50">
                    傳統保健品高達 80% 的營養成分無法被有效吸收。Neumi 採用 <span class="text-yellow-400 font-bold">HydraStat™ 傳輸技術</span>，將關鍵營養精準送達細胞。我們的成果就是最好的證明——臨床試驗驗證、數千則見證、社群熱烈迴響。
                </p>
            </div>
            <a href="https://line.me/ti/p/~makto2019" class="inline-block bg-yellow-400 hover:bg-yellow-300 text-indigo-900 font-bold text-xl px-10 py-4 rounded-full transition duration-300 shadow-lg transform hover:scale-105">
                立即加入諮詢
            </a>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="py-16 px-6 bg-white">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-indigo-900 mb-10 text-center">奈米技術與生物利用度的革命</h2>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <div class="bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-indigo-700 mb-4">奈米化定義</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600">將大分子分解成 < 100 奈米微粒，確保真正的奈米級吸收，而非傳統微米技術。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-indigo-700 mb-4">生物利用度</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600">大幅提升營養吸收率，讓身體與細胞能迅速、充分地利用關鍵營養素。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-indigo-700 mb-4">快速吸收</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600">奈米型穀胱甘肽在放入口中時即開始吸收，效果遠超傳統產品。</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-16 px-6 bg-slate-50">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-12">
            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border-l-8 border-indigo-500">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-indigo-900 mb-3">NutriSwish (口服噴霧)</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-700 text-lg">透過口腔黏膜吸收，極速傳遞營養。耐力運動員每小時補充，能維持穩定水平，防止疲勞並持續產能。</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border-l-8 border-purple-500">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-purple-900 mb-3">Neumi Skin (護膚噴霧)</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-700 text-lg">結合穀胱甘肽、玻尿酸、膠原蛋白，深層滲透肌底，收縮毛孔、撫平細紋，隨時隨地噴灑，簡單護膚。</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-20 px-6 bg-indigo-950 text-white text-center">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">我們幫助團隊打造夢想中的事業</h2>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12 text-left">
                <div class="bg-indigo-900 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-indigo-700">
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-yellow-400 mb-2">AI 自動化系統</h4>
                    <p class="text-indigo-100">用系統放大成果、複製成功，讓陌生開發、跟進、成交與團隊擴展變得更簡單。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-indigo-900 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-indigo-700">
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-yellow-400 mb-2">建立被動收入</h4>
                    <p class="text-indigo-100">不必手動苦苦開發，利用 AI 放大影響力，建立一套真正能運作的自動化事業。</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <a href="https://line.me/ti/p/~makto2019" class="inline-block bg-yellow-400 hover:bg-yellow-300 text-indigo-950 font-black text-2xl px-12 py-5 rounded-full shadow-2xl transition duration-300 transform hover:scale-105">
                立即與我聯絡
            </a>
            <p class="text-lg text-indigo-300 font-bold mt-6">Line ID: makto2019</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="bg-indigo-950 text-indigo-500 py-8 text-center border-t border-indigo-900">
        <p>Copyright © 2026 Neumi | 欣美 | 樂享系統 | All Rights Reserved.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>